      "abstract": "To amend sections 4511.092, 4511.093, 4511.096, 4511.097, 4511.098, 4511.099, and 4511.0911; to enact new section 4511.094; and to repeal sections 4511.094, 4511.095, 4511.0912, 4511.0913, and 4511.0914 of the Revised Code to require elector approval for a municipal traffic camera program and to streamline the traffic camera laws."
